The '''Strategy Center''', formerly known as the '''War Room''', was a communications and planning center of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] on the [[Yavin 4/Legends|fourth]] [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Yavin Prime/Legends|Yavin]]. Located in the center of the second level of the [[Great Temple/Legends|Great Temple]], the War Room resided directly below the main command center.

During the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], [[General/Legends|General]] [[Jan Dodonna/Legends|Jan Dodonna]], [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]], and [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] gathered in the War Room. From within, they listened to the communications between [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] as the battle unfolded around the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]].

The War Room was briefly attacked and occupied by Imperial forces during the Empire's [[Attack on Yavin 4]], but they were defeated by then-Commander Skywalker and Wedge Antilles of Red Squadron, when trying to reach General Dodonna and surviving Rebel personnel in Yavin Base.

After [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] created the [[Jedi Praxeum]], the War Room was renamed the Strategy Center.

